Social features
My WCCM - Powered by Mighty Networks
My WCCM
What is my WCCM?
My WCCM is a public social community network hosted on the platform Mighty Networks. The
network itself is free and accessible to anyone, though certain areas such as paid offerings or
retreats are accessible only to those who purchase them.
What data does the WCCM collect?
The only information that WCCM collects from Members is their name, email address,
purchases or enrollment history, and responses to surveys. Any information you post in your
profile or public feed will be visible to anyone who visits the network while information shared
in private groups or private messages will be visible only to you and the recipients.
What data do Mighty Networks collect?
The only information that Mighty Networks collects from Members is IP Address and mobile
device ID. They need this information so that they know where to send responses to users’
page requests. They also use it to determine users’ general geographic location. As part of
Mighty Networks General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) compliance effort provides a
summary of how they collect, use, and share personal data.
This processing constitutes:
a Sharing in California
